Quickstrike:
 
 
Quickstrike quickly stood up and nearly leaped out of the cell. He looked around and replied to Dark Mouse: "Sure, ah'm fine." He was a little surly about being locked up. He turned his head and glowered at Black Arachnia. 
"Why did ya lock me up in that thing?"  he asked her.

She looked at Quickstrike, and had a look of consern on her face.
"Are you alright commander?"
